{"tid":1038204,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU出席粉絲畢業禮送禮物花了多少錢？156份禮物花費$1700萬","createTime":"2019-02-26T13:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T13:22:34.000Z","uid":34643,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"94f08bf90344832c42d2bf210a6d3a359b669d6c","tid":1038204,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709637.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709637.png&h=11a46c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n說到IU寵粉絲，那真的是三天三夜都講不完啊！ 最近IU就遵守了和幸運粉絲的約定，出席了她的畢業典禮。<br />\n<br />\nIU去年的一場粉絲會上和粉絲約定參加她的畢業典禮。 為了遵守約定，IU在特意前往了金濟，還給當天畢業的學生們送上了禮物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709638.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709638.png&h=c8847e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業典禮上IU不僅親口呼喊了那位小粉絲的名字，更演唱了《你的意義》和《BBIBBI》慶祝學生們順利畢業。她還為自己的小粉絲准備了香水、花束和身體乳作為禮物，稱這是她最愛的香水。 此外IU也沒有忘記其他的畢業生，精心準備了花束、化妝品和巧克力送給大家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709639.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709639.png&h=042e7e13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709640.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709640.png&h=7f0008f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要以為這些東西很便宜，事後就有粉絲公開了禮物的價格，花束、化妝品和巧克力的價格分別為61000韓幣、49500韓幣和10580韓幣，一個人禮物的總價就有12.7萬韓幣之多。 而當天畢業的學生有156人，為準備他們的禮物，IU就花了1700多萬韓幣。 即使是大量批發有折扣，IU也至少花了1000萬以上，實在是大手筆，寵粉太厲害！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709641.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709641.png&h=b3aa086f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-02-25/114297-709642.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-02-25%2F114297-709642.png&h=3d250f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這麼用心準備的禮物，相比畢業生們就算不是IU的粉絲，內心也會感動不已吧！<br />\n<br />\n「圖：PANN」"},{"pid":"39a5507ab79f44a89f83f5f9ee725a4268f6b491","tid":1038204,"uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想要iu d老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311f6f2687ba71715fc1ef641cd30ceb0357d154","tid":1038204,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"天使?"},{"pid":"f0ca38b47eec342ef5f3e0f842d72ff2f96dbaee","tid":1038204,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a5507ab79f44a89f83f5f9ee725a4268f6b491","tid":1038204,"uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想要iu d老泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:36:11.000Z","msg":"咪FF啦 我奶緊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089d2074819964549f3e8fa770db885a6c33a0a4","tid":1038204,"uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"311f6f2687ba71715fc1ef641cd30ceb0357d154","tid":1038204,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:28:21.000Z","msg":"天使?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DmVWm_1XoAMpCwS.jpg:orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDmVWm_1XoAMpCwS.jpg%3Aorig&h=ef411066&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84003b814f9a4ca0a9e86b720c2b5228c47270d4","tid":1038204,"uid":236891,"like":3,"dislike":26,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"089d2074819964549f3e8fa770db885a6c33a0a4","tid":1038204,"uid":34643,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score